For sale: $410,000. RARE OPPORTUNITY!  TURN KEY BUSINESS "SERENITY LODGE" , FURNITURE, AND PROPERTY

How would you like to own your own personal retreat in the middle of the Superior National Forest, escape from the day to day rat race whenever you feel like it and at the same time be producing a passive side income? After 5 years in business, the owner is relocating and is putting this gem on the market. Return clientele, website, fully licensed by county and health department (which would need to be re-licensed under new ownership), watercraft, furniture and reliable operational staff. More enticing is the separate large 2 car garage on the property with an above bunk house with electricity and potential for heating. There is also another separate 2 stall garage space that remains unfinished and could be developed to meet your specific needs.

description: For sale: $179,900. Baptism River in your front yard! Gorgeous 4 season river views from nearly every window of your 3 bedroom home in convenient Finland location. Perfect for year round or recreation use with snowmobile trails nearby and a designated trout stream in your yard. Cozy 3 bedroom home features an eat-in kitchen, separate dining area open to a spacious living room with refinished maple floors. Main floor bedroom plus 2 additional bedrooms upstairs. Nice, clean basement with updated furnace and electric. Newer well and compliant septic system. Situated on a level 2 acre lot with room for family camping and recreation.
